item.description:
         DaoJones provides a search API to find documents in the database. You do not need to create any formula language.

Copy the following lines into the try-catch block within the main method:

-----------------------------------

final FieldSearchCriterion<String> sc = new FieldSearchCriterion<String>("subject", StringComparison.STARTSWITH_IGNORECASE, "DaoJones");

final Task task = con.find(sc);

System.out.println(task.getSubject());
